    "Add words or short phrases to improve speech recognition accuracy for specialized terminology. Vocabulary is saved per source language." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the purpose of the custom vocabulary feature.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "専門用語の音声認識精度を向上させるために、単語や短いフレーズを追加してください。語彙はソース言語ごとに保存されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
